        <li>Mature Scrum and Kanban</li>
        <li>Active development and frequent updates</li>
        <li>Growing community and ecosystem</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Jira Cons</h3>
    <div class="cons-box">
      <ul>
        <li>Can be slow with large projects</li>
        <li>Complex and overwhelming</li>
        <li>Steep learning curve</li>
        <li>Expensive at scale</li>
        <li>Administration overhead</li>
        <li>Interface can feel overwhelming initially</li>
        <li>Premium features require higher tier plans</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Who Should Use Which?</h2>
    <p><strong>Choose Linear</strong> if you want a fast modern project management tool and value speed and simplicity.</p>
    <p><strong>Choose Jira</strong> if you need enterprise-grade customization, extensive reporting, and complex workflows.</p>

